What is a Client?
-It's a laptop.
-A users personal machine that makes requests of the server.

Clients and Servers work together. Clients make requests of the server.

Computers can be servers too. 

Servers live in dedicated hardware intended to handle ALL the request and repsonses of many clients

Creating a server equates to writing code that handeles what the server will do.

